    "(Indexing and Slicing arrays) Create an array containing the values 1–15, reshape it into a 3-by-5 array, then use indexing and slicing techniques to perform each of the following operations: [implement operations (a) to (c) twice, once with positive indexing and once with negative indexing]:\n",
